The paper presents an algorithm for mining OWL 2 EL class expressions from online RDF datasets, which involves techniques from artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML) to build a smart index and iterate over it. The algorithm also proposes a transformation function to RDF Data Shapes, which relates to database (DB) and semantic web (LG) technologies. The paper targets ontology engineers, which falls under software engineering (SE) and cybersecurity (CYBER) domains.
